🚀 Excited to Share My Power BI Project! 📊
I’m happy to showcase my latest project — Mobile Sales Data Dashboard built using Power BI.
This interactive dashboard provides deep insights into mobile sales performance and helps in making data-driven decisions.
🔍 Key Highlights of the Dashboard:
 ✅ Total Sales Analysis across multiple cities
 ✅ Monthly & Daily Sales Trends 📅
 ✅ Brand-wise Performance (Apple, Samsung, OnePlus, Vivo, etc.)
 ✅ Payment Method Insights (UPI, Cards, Cash) 💳

 ✅ Sales by Mobile Models 📱
 ✅ Customer Rating Analysis (Good, Average, Poor)
 ✅ MTD (Month-to-Date) & Yearly Comparison with Previous Year
📈 What I Learned:
Data Cleaning & Transformation
Data Modeling in Power BI
Creating Interactive Visualizations
Using DAX for calculated measures
Building business insights from raw data
💡 This project helped me strengthen my skills in data analysis and visualization, and I’m excited to work on more real-world datasets.
